message: Enhance report generation script: add duration parsing function to HTML report rendering, improving the accuracy of displayed test durations. This update ensures that duration data is correctly processed and included in the generated reports.

Enhance report generation script and GitHub Actions workflow: implement a line chart for visualizing test durations in HTML reports, improving data representation. Update CSS styles for data points and labels to enhance user interaction and clarity. Add grid lines to the chart for better readability and integrate build duration calculation in the workflow for accurate reporting.

Refactor report generation script and GitHub Actions workflow: update max duration calculation to use a namespace for improved clarity, enhance error handling in the script execution, and simplify build duration handling in the workflow for better maintainability.

Refactor report generation script and GitHub Actions workflow: adjust CSS styles for history grid in HTML reports to enhance visual clarity and user experience. Update Slack notification format to include detailed test run information, improving communication of test results.

Enhance report generation script: add visual history grid to HTML reports, improving the display of test results with interactive elements for better user experience. Include status indicators for each report and placeholders for missing data.

Add GitHub Actions script for generating Playwright test reports: implement a dedicated Python script to create HTML reports, manage report history, and streamline report generation process. Update workflow to utilize the new script, ensuring proper environment variable handling and script execution.

Update GitHub Actions workflow: change permissions for contents to write, specify GitHub token for checkout, and reintroduce Git configuration for user details during commit to ensure proper attribution in gh-pages updates.
